/behold-the-dallas-based-underdog-candidate-of-the-2020-presidential-election/ |accessdate=16 February 2020 |work=D Magazine |last1=Shinneman|first1=Shawn|date=5 February 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Transhumanist Party]]\n|'''[[Johannon Ben Zion]]'''<br>Filmmaker from [[Arizona]]\n|'''Charlie Kam'''<br>Author from [[California]]\n|TBD\n|TBD\n|<ref>{{cite tweet|user=USTranshumanist|number=1179585085583970304|title=The U.S. Transhumanist Party / Transhuman Party (USTP) announces the results of its 2019 Electronic Primary for the USTP\u2019s endorsement of a candidate to run for President of the United States. https://transhumanist-party.org/2019/10/02/ustp-2019-electronic-primary-results/ Congratulations to Johannon Ben Zion for a strong victory!|date=October 2, 2019|author=[[Transhumanist Party]]|accessdate=April 16, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Unity Party of America]]\n|'''Bill Hammons'''<br>Founder of the Unity Party from [[Colorado]]\n|'''Eric Bodenstab'''<br>Unity Party State Chairman from [[Colorado]]\n|TBD\n|TBD\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://billisrunning.com/hammons-campaign-releases/declaration-president-vp/|title=Hammons Declares For President & Bodenstab Declares For VP|date=March 23, 2020|first=Eric|last=Bodenstab|work=Bill for President|accessdate=April 17, 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n<!--***Candidates who have Wikipedia pages and have stated that they will run for president on a source other than social media can be listed below-->\nNotable people who have announced that they are running for president in 2020 as independent or minor party candidates but have not established campaign websites are:\n*[[Perry Caravello]], actor and comedian from California<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.simplydonthepodcast.com/2019/05/19/the-213th-podcast/|title=The 213th Podcast|website=Simply Don}}</ref>\n*[[VoiceoverPete|Pete Accetturo]], [[YouTube]] personality from [[Florida]]<ref>{{Cite news|last=Kvatum|first=Lia|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/magazine/hundreds-of